By default all the required should be placed under webapp -> WEB-INF -> lib ->place the jars
Working action attribute of <form>
Case:1 <form action="reg.do">
http://localhost:8080/mywebapp/reg.do  (request will be submitted to current app(mywebapp))
Case:2 <form action="/reg.do">
http://localhost:8080/reg.do  (request will be submitted to root of tomcat)
Case:3<form action="/mywebapp/reg.do">
http://localhost:8080/reg.do   (request will be submitted to mywebapp)
Case:4 <form action="https://www.facebook.com"> (request will be submitted to facebook.com)

